FBIS4-8535 "dreeu072_k_94002" FBIS-EEU-94-072 Daily Report 13 Apr 1994 CROATIA Tudjman Receives International Mediators Tudjman Receives International Mediators LD1304140294 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 1300 GMT 13 Apr 94 LD1304140294 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Excerpt] Croatian President Dr. Franjo Tudjman today received in Zagreb Geert Ahrens and Kai Eide, ambassadors to the International Conference on the Former Yugoslavia, the president's office has announced. They are discussing the resumption of talks with local Serbs. President Tudjman again stressed that these talks could not be held outside Croatia. [passage omitted]
